                <h1 class="domdom">20</h1>

                <h1>Event: <a href="/on/event/273">Diy Film Reviews Launch Event: Top Uk Film Magazine In Newcastle: Little White Lies</a></h1>

                <h2>20 Mar 2010, 11 a.m.</h2>

                <p>Little White Lies is by far one of the most interesting, ambitious, passionate, genuine and beautiful film magazines in the UK. We are extremely proud to be welcoming the Publisher and the Editor of Little White Lies at the Cinema, to give a talk, to launch the Northern Lights Film Festival, and the DIY film review project.
</p>

